						<div class="block-21 mb-4 d-flex">
							<a class="blog-img mr-4" style="background-image: url(images/image_3.jpg);"></a>
							<div class="text">
								<h3 class="heading"><a href="#">Even the all-powerful Pointing has no control about the
										blind texts</a>
								</h3>
								<div class="meta">
